######## THE POINT ########
If A has the highest p in the table and an impossible weight,
then p-value ranking is not model selection.
Per Flegontov et al. (2025): out-of-[0,1] weights on a landscape are
SYMMETRY statements -- the target lies beyond a source on a cline.
